              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>We assume functions to be permanent capabilities (by design), roles to be occasional capabilities (used in some situations), keeping those capabilities in a single terminology.</lexicalForm>
